1:解压缩tomcat.tar.gz
2:在tomcat->bin->startup.sh添加环境变量
  JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jdk/jdk1.8.0_151
  JRE_HOME=${JAVA_HOME}/jre
  PATH=${JAVA_HOME}/bin:$PATH
  CLASSPATH=.:${JAVA_HOME}/lib/dt.jar:${JAVA_HOME}/lib/tools.jar
  TOMCAT_HOME=/opt/tomcat/apache-tomcat-9.0.4

3:打开关闭脚本添加startup.sh相同配置
4:开启关闭tomcat
 ./startup.sh
5浏览器输入 localhost:8080
